This app has been updated by Apple to use the latest Apple signing certificate.

What ISN'T new?! The latest Cult of Mac Magazine is a ground-up rebuild and redesign of the Cult of Mac Magazine you love, with added animations, gorgeous graphics, and incredible new user interface that will have you swiping and tapping to get to all the amazing content you've come to expect from this first-class digital magazine.
